Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Senior Full Stack Engineer position with Zendesk. I bring over three years of professional experience building production-grade backend systems, real-time AI platforms, and full-stack applications, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

