I have always been passionate about building customer experiences that are painless, frictionless, and more helpful, and I am excited about Zendesk's mission to simplify the complexity of business and make it easy for companies and customers to create meaningful connections. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

